    <h1 class="fio-h1">How to Use the Finviz Stock Screener</h1>
    <p class="fio-p">
      Finviz (short for <em>Financial Visualizations</em>) is a fast way to scan thousands of stocks using
      <strong>descriptive</strong>, <strong>fundamental</strong>, and <strong>technical</strong> filters.
      This lesson shows you how to build screens that surface better options setups without wasting time.
    </p>
    <p class="fio-p fio-note fio-muted">
      Start here: <a href="https://finviz.com"><strong>finviz.com</strong></a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 1 -->
  <div class="fio-card">
    <h2 class="fio-h2">1) Access the Screener</h2>
    <ul class="fio-list">
      <li>
        <span class="fio-check" aria-hidden="true">
