  <!-- PART 2 -->
  <div class="fio-card">
    <h2 class="fio-h2">Part 2: Filter Strategies</h2>
    <p class="fio-p fio-note fio-muted">
      Below are simple “plug-and-play” filter stacks you can copy. Start with General → add Fundamentals → finish with Technical.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- GENERAL FILTERS -->
  <div class="fio-card fio-soft">
    <h3 class="fio-h3">1) General Screening Filters</h3>
    <ol class="fio-list">
      <li><strong>Price:</strong> Over $5 (or Over $10) — filters out penny-stock chaos.</li>
      <li><strong>Average Volume:</strong> Over 500K (or Over 1M) — improves fills + reduces slippage.</li>
      <li><strong>Market Cap:</strong> Over $300M (or Over $1B) — focuses on more stable companies.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <!-- FUNDAMENTAL FILTERS -->
  <div class="fio-card">
    <h3 class="fio-h3">2) Fundamental Filters</h3>
    <ol class="fio-list">
      <li><strong>P/E:</strong> Under 20–25 (avoids overpaying).</li>
      <li><strong>PEG:</strong> Under 1.0–1.5 (growth at a reasonable price).</li>
      <li><strong>EPS Growth (Past 5Y):</strong> Over 10–20% (proven growth).</li>
      <li><strong>EPS Growth (Next 5Y):</strong> Over 10–15% (future potential).</li>
      <li><strong>ROE:</strong> Over 10–15% (quality businesses).</li>
      <li><strong>Debt/Equity:</strong> Under 0.5–1.0 (safer balance sheets).</li>
      <li><strong>Profit Margin:</strong> Over 10% (pricing power).</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <!-- TECHNICAL FILTERS -->
  <div class="fio-card fio-soft">
    <h3 class="fio-h3">3) Technical Filters</h3>
    <ol class="fio-list">
      <li><strong>Price above SMA50</strong> (shorter-term trend).</li>
      <li><strong>Price above SMA200</strong> (long-term trend).</li>
      <li><strong>RSI:</strong> &lt; 30 = oversold, &gt; 70 = overbought.</li>
      <li><strong>Candlestick patterns:</strong> hammer / engulfing if you use pattern signals.</li>
      <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Up over the last month or quarter (momentum screens).</li>
    </ol>

    <figure class="wp-block-image">
      <img src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdHwT1oD22JFVs4RMoFocV-HBhQlsdgTDTYXNEhARWz6Px4Uafo_bVMD2HJlCjpV2RG_Q-ZiCX78GA-BbauUp7UV3QiNwV92liFFJnGklFehPYMs2X3n_dAl-tJXS76fqCNMOJpIg?key=EHal6qEyYjyaJ7OatsBxDXiW" alt="Finviz technical filters example 1" />
    </figure>

    <figure class="wp-block-image">
      <img src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcrOCrFld2Q84Nc4LFNNAcElKH4dwZteAI1B38cPW_YKd-yEFw8JeIymSISqcxAduprc_WavIwFKkI-mh6OzfDLT6Tjs15FlnaKlARrPvFUw0m1LotG1MF9frtTgf7ninSuMW4g9w?key=EHal6qEyYjyaJ7OatsBxDXiW" alt="Finviz technical filters example 2" />
    </figure>
  </div>

  <!-- COMBOS -->
  <div class="fio-card">
    <h3 class="fio-h3">4) Combining Filters for Different Strategies</h3>

    <div class="fio-grid2">
      <div class="fio-mini">
        <h4 class="fio-h4">Growth-Focused</h4>
        <ul class="fio-list">
          <li>P/E: Under 25</li>
          <li>EPS Growth (Past 5Y): Over 15%</li>
          <li>Price: Over $10</li>
          <li>Average Volume: Over 500K</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="fio-mini">
        <h4 class="fio-h4">Value-Focused</h4>
        <ul class="fio-list">
          <li>P/E: Under 15</li>
          <li>PEG: Under 1.5</li>
          <li>Debt/Equity: Under 0.5</li>
          <li>Market Cap: Over $1B</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="fio-mini">
        <h4 class="fio-h4">Momentum-Focused</h4>
        <ul class="fio-list">
          <li>Price above SMA50 and SMA200</li>
          <li>Performance (Quarter): Up</li>
          <li>Average Volume: Over 1M</li>
          <li>RSI(14): 40–70 (trend, not overbought)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

